    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the info. it just feels weird having all this money just sitting there in a middle-man account instead of me having control over it. it's like i'm just handing over my cash to a third party to guard it for me. is there anything i should watch out for with these third parties? like how do i know they aren't just sitting on the money or mishandling it?",
