      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your concerns are valid, as escrow accounts do involve third-party management. To minimize risks, it's essential to work with a reputable escrow company or title agent that is licensed and bonded. Ensure they also have a clear commitment to applying funds promptly and accurately to your expenses. You can also review the escrow agreement to see how funds are dispersed and under what circumstances they might be held.",
